{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/work/jekyll-themes/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Jekyll themes","date":"2017-03-30T00:00:00.000Z","date_pretty":"March 30th, 2017","date_from_now":"3 years ago","last_modified_at":"2020-01-13T21:02:39.000Z","last_modified_at_from_now":"6 months ago","path":"/work/jekyll-themes/","author":null,"excerpt":"Open source Jekyll themes to help build a site or blog on GitHub Pages, Netlify, and more.","tags":["Jekyll","web development","design","open source","GitHub"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"aspectRatio":1.7741935483870968,"src":"/static/4b7d6a15f1b4ba25cbc8ce68e163b8eb/fc20c/jekyll-themes-feature.jpg","srcSet":"/static/4b7d6a15f1b4ba25cbc8ce68e163b8eb/6e883/jekyll-themes-feature.jpg 275w,\n/static/4b7d6a15f1b4ba25cbc8ce68e163b8eb/a09ef/jekyll-themes-feature.jpg 550w,\n/static/4b7d6a15f1b4ba25cbc8ce68e163b8eb/fc20c/jekyll-themes-feature.jpg 1100w,\n/static/4b7d6a15f1b4ba25cbc8ce68e163b8eb/4883f/jekyll-themes-feature.jpg 1619w","sizes":"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px"},"fixed":{"src":"/static/4b7d6a15f1b4ba25cbc8ce68e163b8eb/fc20c/jekyll-themes-feature.jpg","height":619,"width":1100}}},"toc":null,"comments":false,"comments_locked":true,"hide_meta":true},"id":"e9376214-3d1a-5cb9-98ae-0c32d4a2e2b0","html":"<p>Below are the Jekyll starters I’ve developed and open sourced. Each theme contains the <code class=\"language-text\">_layouts</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">_includes</code>, Sass/CSS, JavaScript, and other sample files needed to build and host a site or blog. </p>\n<p>The basic setup for each of my themes is roughly the same:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Install <a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com/docs/themes/#understanding-gem-based-themes\">gem-based theme</a>, <a href=\"https://github.com/benbalter/jekyll-remote-theme\">remote theme</a>, or fork the theme repository you’d like to use.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://bundler.io\">Install Bundler</a> <code class=\"language-text\">gem install bundler</code> and run <code class=\"language-text\">bundle install</code> to install all dependencies (Jekyll, plugins, and so on).</li>\n<li>Update <code class=\"language-text\">_config.yml</code>, data files (found in <code class=\"language-text\">_data</code>), and replace sample posts and pages with your own.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>For more specifics, review each theme’s documentation by clicking on the <strong>setup guide</strong> buttons below.</p>\n<h2 id=\"so-simple-theme\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#so-simple-theme\" aria-label=\"so simple theme permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/work/so-simple-jekyll-theme/\">So Simple theme</a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.36363636363636%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"So Simple Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        title=\"So Simple Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        data-src=\"/static/30b43dc1bdc5fdde5583f0edd8b5da24/eacc7/jekyll-theme-so-simple-feature.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/30b43dc1bdc5fdde5583f0edd8b5da24/16841/jekyll-theme-so-simple-feature.jpg 275w,\n/static/30b43dc1bdc5fdde5583f0edd8b5da24/50c97/jekyll-theme-so-simple-feature.jpg 550w,\n/static/30b43dc1bdc5fdde5583f0edd8b5da24/eacc7/jekyll-theme-so-simple-feature.jpg 1100w,\n/static/30b43dc1bdc5fdde5583f0edd8b5da24/cc4ba/jekyll-theme-so-simple-feature.jpg 1650w,\n/static/30b43dc1bdc5fdde5583f0edd8b5da24/4d82d/jekyll-theme-so-simple-feature.jpg 1746w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>So Simple is a Jekyll theme for your words and pictures. Features include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Available as a <a href=\"https://rubygems.org/gems/jekyll-theme-so-simple\">gem-based theme</a> and remote theme.</li>\n<li>Compatible with GitHub Pages.</li>\n<li>A variety of layouts with clean and readable typography.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://microformats.org/wiki/microformats2\">Microformats</a> markup to make post content machine-readable and discoverable.</li>\n<li>Disqus Comments and Google Analytics support.</li>\n<li>SEO best practices via <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/jekyll-seo-tag\">Jekyll SEO Tag</a>.</li>\n<li>Options to customize the theme and make it your own.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/mmistakes/so-simple-theme\" class=\"btn\">Setup guide</a>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/so-simple-theme/\" class=\"btn\">Theme preview</a>\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"basically-basic-theme\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#basically-basic-theme\" aria-label=\"basically basic theme permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/work/basically-basic-jekyll-theme/\">Basically Basic theme</a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.36363636363636%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"Basically Basic Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        title=\"Basically Basic Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        data-src=\"/static/23d71c3eb33cf7e7c475822546ca7ade/eacc7/jekyll-theme-basically-basic-feature.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/23d71c3eb33cf7e7c475822546ca7ade/16841/jekyll-theme-basically-basic-feature.jpg 275w,\n/static/23d71c3eb33cf7e7c475822546ca7ade/50c97/jekyll-theme-basically-basic-feature.jpg 550w,\n/static/23d71c3eb33cf7e7c475822546ca7ade/eacc7/jekyll-theme-basically-basic-feature.jpg 1100w,\n/static/23d71c3eb33cf7e7c475822546ca7ade/8f439/jekyll-theme-basically-basic-feature.jpg 1234w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Basically Basic is a <a href=\"https://jekyllrb.com/docs/themes/\">Jekyll theme</a> meant as a substitute for the default — <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/minima\">Minima</a>. Conventions and features found there are fully supported by <strong>Basically Basic</strong>, with a few enhancements thrown in for good measure:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Available as a <a href=\"https://rubygems.org/gems/jekyll-theme-basically-basic\">gem-based theme</a> and remote theme.</li>\n<li>Compatible with GitHub Pages.</li>\n<li>Clean responsive design with six customizable skins.</li>\n<li>Curriculum Vitæ/Resume layout powered by <a href=\"http://registry.jsonresume.org/\">JSON data</a>.</li>\n<li>About page layout.</li>\n<li>Disqus Comments and Google Analytics support.</li>\n<li>SEO best practices via <a href=\"https://github.com/jekyll/jekyll-seo-tag/\">Jekyll SEO Tag</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/mmistakes/jekyll-theme-basically-basic\" class=\"btn\">Setup guide</a>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/jekyll-theme-basically-basic/\" class=\"btn\">Theme preview</a>\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"minimal-mistakes-theme\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#minimal-mistakes-theme\" aria-label=\"minimal mistakes theme permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/work/minimal-mistakes-jekyll-theme/\">Minimal Mistakes theme</a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.36363636363636%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"Minimal Mistakes Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        title=\"Minimal Mistakes Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        data-src=\"/static/fdfedffa0cd9f1b85baa15ef43451be7/eacc7/minimal-mistakes-3-feature.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/fdfedffa0cd9f1b85baa15ef43451be7/16841/minimal-mistakes-3-feature.jpg 275w,\n/static/fdfedffa0cd9f1b85baa15ef43451be7/50c97/minimal-mistakes-3-feature.jpg 550w,\n/static/fdfedffa0cd9f1b85baa15ef43451be7/eacc7/minimal-mistakes-3-feature.jpg 1100w,\n/static/fdfedffa0cd9f1b85baa15ef43451be7/490e5/minimal-mistakes-3-feature.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>A flexible two-column Jekyll theme with a minimalist aesthetic.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Bundled as a “theme gem” for easier installation/upgrading.</li>\n<li>Support for Jekyll’s built-in Sass/SCSS preprocessor.</li>\n<li>Nine different skins (color variations).</li>\n<li>Optional <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/layouts/#headers\">header images</a>, <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/layouts/#sidebars\">custom sidebars</a>, <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/helpers/#table-of-contents\">table of contents</a>, <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/helpers/#gallery\">galleries</a>, related posts, <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/configuration/#breadcrumb-navigation-beta\">breadcrumb links</a>, <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/helpers/#navigation-list\">navigation lists</a>, and more.</li>\n<li>Commenting support (powered by <a href=\"https://disqus.com/\">Disqus</a>, <a href=\"https://developers.facebook.com/docs/plugins/comments\">Facebook</a>, Google+, <a href=\"https://www.discourse.org/\">Discourse</a>, static-based via <a href=\"https://staticman.net/\">Staticman</a>, and <a href=\"https://utteranc.es/\">utterances</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/quick-start-guide/\" class=\"btn\">Setup guide</a>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/\" class=\"btn\">Theme preview</a>\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"hpstr-theme\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hpstr-theme\" aria-label=\"hpstr theme permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/work/hpstr-jekyll-theme/\">HPSTR theme</a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.36363636363636%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"HPSTR Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        title=\"HPSTR Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        data-src=\"/static/8b4c06214b5f78b2db7ae49a28641f3a/eacc7/hpstr-preview-feature.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/8b4c06214b5f78b2db7ae49a28641f3a/16841/hpstr-preview-feature.jpg 275w,\n/static/8b4c06214b5f78b2db7ae49a28641f3a/50c97/hpstr-preview-feature.jpg 550w,\n/static/8b4c06214b5f78b2db7ae49a28641f3a/eacc7/hpstr-preview-feature.jpg 1100w,\n/static/8b4c06214b5f78b2db7ae49a28641f3a/b2d41/hpstr-preview-feature.jpg 1632w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>A responsive Jekyll blog theme designed to give your site a modern and somewhat cliché feel.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with GitHub Pages.</li>\n<li>Modern design with rounded rectangles and subtle gradients.</li>\n<li>Animated main menu.</li>\n<li>Built-in support for Sass and data files (requires Jekyll 2.x).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/jekyll-theme-hpstr/theme-setup/\" class=\"btn\">Setup guide</a>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/jekyll-theme-hpstr/\" class=\"btn\">Theme preview</a>\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"skinny-bones-theme\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#skinny-bones-theme\" aria-label=\"skinny bones theme permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"/work/skinny-bones-jekyll/\">Skinny Bones theme</a></h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; background-color: var(--input-background-color); max-width: 1100px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.36363636363636%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image lazyload\"\n        alt=\"Skinny Bones Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        title=\"Skinny Bones Jekyll theme screenshot\"\n        data-src=\"/static/f6f11b2723d3bc05992c09211de879e1/eacc7/skinny-bones-preview-feature.jpg\"\n        data-srcset=\"/static/f6f11b2723d3bc05992c09211de879e1/16841/skinny-bones-preview-feature.jpg 275w,\n/static/f6f11b2723d3bc05992c09211de879e1/50c97/skinny-bones-preview-feature.jpg 550w,\n/static/f6f11b2723d3bc05992c09211de879e1/eacc7/skinny-bones-preview-feature.jpg 1100w,\n/static/f6f11b2723d3bc05992c09211de879e1/f0a7a/skinny-bones-preview-feature.jpg 1418w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>A Jekyll starter based off of an older incarnation of Made Mistakes.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Compatible with GitHub Pages.</li>\n<li>Built-in support for Sass and data files (requires Jekyll 2.x).</li>\n<li>Off canvas menu.</li>\n<li>Tile based archives.</li>\n<li>Optional table of contents, share links, Disqus comments modules, and more.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/jekyll-theme-skinny-bones/getting-started/\" class=\"btn\">Setup guide</a>\n  <a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/jekyll-theme-skinny-bones/\" class=\"btn\">Theme guide</a>\n</p>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"license\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#license\" aria-label=\"license permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>License</h3>\n<p>These themes are free and open source software, distributed under the MIT License. Feel free to modify them to suit your needs.</p>","excerpt":"Below are the Jekyll starters I’ve developed and open sourced. Each theme contains the , , Sass/CSS, JavaScript, and other sample files…","timeToRead":4,"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/work/jekyll-themes/#so-simple-theme\">So Simple theme</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/work/jekyll-themes/#basically-basic-theme\">Basically Basic theme</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/work/jekyll-themes/#minimal-mistakes-theme\">Minimal Mistakes theme</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/work/jekyll-themes/#hpstr-theme\">HPSTR theme</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/work/jekyll-themes/#skinny-bones-theme\">Skinny Bones theme</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/work/jekyll-themes/#license\">License</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"comments":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"001f3f28-41cb-5c23-a02d-a332a7b701a4","frontmatter":{"name":"Sergio","email":"53afaf67d940adcc68dae02590df75d1","friendlyDate":"August 31, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-08-31T01:55:06.632Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Great job! You are doing amazing stuff. Happy to learn from you.</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"c3b6c528-5231-5657-9785-7a10e0c3aba6","frontmatter":{"name":"Nghi Nguyen","email":"8c5e5237fe7ddc1e13e6ae13b9c133bb","friendlyDate":"September 10, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-09-10T04:41:59.854Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Hi Michael. I’m upgrading my site which is based on Phlow’s Feeling Responsive;\nI figured the best way is to do that is to simply migrate my small site over to\nthe code based on mademistakes. It’s an awesome site. There is though one thing\nI can’t figure out how to do which is to get a large header like this:\n<a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/layout-header-image-text-readability/\">https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/layout-header-image-text-readability/</a>.</p>\n<p>As an aside, though I started out looking for a way to upgrade my site’s\nFoundation code, I discover a whole new world of painting on the iPad. I now got\na 53 pencil and Procreate. Thank you for sharing with the world your very own\nbeautiful world. You’ve made us all so much richer.</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"cc4daa07-3d1e-52cb-ac37-e9cf61613077","frontmatter":{"name":"Michael Rose","email":"1ce71bc10b86565464b612093d89707e","friendlyDate":"September 11, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-09-11T01:15:32.607Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Made Mistakes isn’t the same code base as my Minimal Mistakes theme. Some things\nare similar but not all. It also isn’t that documented since it’s my personal\nsite.</p>\n<p>I’d suggest using Minimal Mistakes since that is released and\n<a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/quick-start-guide/\">documented</a>\nas a full fledged theme.</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"3ad5e427-23dd-5ab2-925b-3b368a03ac94","frontmatter":{"name":"Nghi Nguyen","email":"8c5e5237fe7ddc1e13e6ae13b9c133bb","friendlyDate":"September 11, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-09-11T01:55:17.238Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Yes, you’ve convinced me. It looks like it has everything I wanted, and more.\nThank you so much.</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"63baf3c5-f60f-561b-8ec0-921b6ba06df7","frontmatter":{"name":"Frédéric Letellier","email":"fda5a0af300f7d6762f26007975d9de6","friendlyDate":"October 27, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-10-27T11:45:48.764Z","published":null},"html":"<p>Minimal Mistakes theme is very good stuff. Can I put a photo on excerpt of posts\n? I try multiple things but i don’t find !</p>"}},{"node":{"id":"31eeb9e7-d957-5901-a3c7-f9a3f91f329c","frontmatter":{"name":"Michael Rose","email":"1ce71bc10b86565464b612093d89707e","friendlyDate":"October 27, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-10-27T15:29:51.735Z","published":null},"html":"<p>@Frédéric - with some hacking of the theme files you can add images to an\narchive listing. I would suggest adding something like\n<code class=\"language-text\">{% if post.image.teaser %}&lt;img src=&quot;{{ post.image.teaser }}&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;{% endif %}</code>\nto\n<a href=\"https://github.com/mmistakes/minimal-mistakes/blob/master/_includes/archive-single.html\"><strong>_includes/archive-single.html</strong></a>\nwhere you’d like the image to appear.</p>\n<p>With some additional CSS to style things how you want and adding the following\nYAML Front Matter to your posts you should be able to do what you want.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">image</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">teaser</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> path<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>to<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>your<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>post<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>image.jpg</code></pre></div>"}},{"node":{"id":"3a85e4fa-9364-5e9f-8050-62590b579c68","frontmatter":{"name":"Michael Rose","email":"1ce71bc10b86565464b612093d89707e","friendlyDate":"October 27, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-10-27T15:44:19.479Z","published":null},"html":"<p>You can also leverage the\n<a href=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/docs/layouts/#grid-view\">“grid” archive type</a>\nif you don’t want to edit any templates.</p>\n<p>Simply change <code class=\"language-text\">{% include archive-single.html %}</code> to\n<code class=\"language-text\">{% include archive-single.html type=&quot;grid&quot; %}</code> in your index pages (eg. the\n<a href=\"https://github.com/mmistakes/minimal-mistakes/blob/master/index.html#L11\">home page</a>)\nand you’ll get a 4 column grid of posts.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://mmistakes.github.io/minimal-mistakes/assets/images/mm-archive-grid-view-example.jpg\" alt=\"grid view screenshot\"></p>"}},{"node":{"id":"21ef0988-0130-53c9-b60d-feb2f51e0e7b","frontmatter":{"name":"Frédéric Letellier","email":"fda5a0af300f7d6762f26007975d9de6","friendlyDate":"October 28, 2016","iso8601Date":"2016-10-28T13:10:45.559Z","published":null},"html":"<p>@Michael Rose Thank you, I have implement the first solution, but the second\nsolution works too ! I think you would say : Simply change\n<code class=\"language-text\">{% if post.image.teaser %}&lt;img src=&quot;{{ post.image.teaser }}&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;{% endif %}</code></p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/work/eko-wave/","title":"Eko Wave","categories":["work"],"tags":["design","web development"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/work/eko-wave.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/work/basically-basic-jekyll-theme/","title":"Basically Basic","categories":["work"],"tags":["Jekyll","web development","design","open source","GitHub"]},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/28041/opensource/github.com/mmistakes/made-mistakes-gatsby/src/posts/work/basically-basic-jekyll-theme.md"}}}}